  "comment": "$$\\sqrt{72}-\\sqrt{288}\\sin^2\\frac{21\\pi}{8}=\\sqrt{72}(1-\\sqrt{4}\\sin^2\\frac{21\\pi}{8})=\\sqrt{72}(1-\\ 2\\sin^2\\frac{21\\pi}{8})$$\nСогласно формуле косинуса двойного угла:\n$$(1-\\ 2\\sin^2\\frac{21\\pi}{8})=\\cos (2\\cdot \\frac{21\\pi}{8})=\\cos \\frac{21\\pi}{4}$$\nПолучим:\n$$6\\sqrt{2}\\cos \\frac{21\\pi}{4}=6\\sqrt{2}\\cos (4\\pi +\\frac{5\\pi}{4})=6\\sqrt{2}\\cos \\frac{5\\pi}{4}=6\\sqrt{2}\\cdot (-\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2})=-6$$\nОтвет: -6",
